+subsection('VegaLiteComponent')
  p.typo__p
    | <kbd>VegaLiteComponent</kbd> - vue component wrapper around <em>vega-lite</em>.
    | For more details refer to
    a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html')  Vega Lit Docs
  .table__container
    table.table.table--full-size.table--fixed
      thead
        tr.table__tr
          th.table__th(width="100") Name
          th.table__th(width="80") Type
          th.table__th(width="180") Default
          th.table__th(width="200") Description
      tbody
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td.utils--center(colspan="4"): strong Props

        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#top-level-specifications') $schema
          td.table__td String
          td.table__td
          td.table__td.
            URL to JSON schema for a Vega-Lite specification.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#common') description
          td.table__td String
          td.table__td
          td.table__td.
            An optional description of this visualization for commenting purpose.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/transform.html') transform
          td.table__td Array
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | The top-level transform object is an array of objects describing transformations
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/data.html') data
          td.table__td Array || Object
          td.table__td: kbd { values: [] }
          td.table__td
            | Tabular data, similar to a spreadsheet or a database table.
            | It passable to pass url but without format and names, default format json
            | In <em>vue-vega</em> we provide a shortcut,
            | so you user can pass `[]` instead of `{ values: [] }`
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#single-view-spec') mark
          td.table__td String||Object
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | Required. A string describing the mark type
            | (one of "bar", "circle", "square", "tick", "line", "area", "point", "rule", and "text")
            | or a mark definition object.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
           a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/encoding.html') encoding
          td.table__td Object
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | An integral part of the data visualization process is encoding data with visual properties of graphical marks.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#top-level-specifications') autoResize
          td.table__td Boolean
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | Resize is a boolean indicating if autosize layout should be re-calculated on every update.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#top-level-specifications') background
          td.table__td String
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | CSS color property to use as the background of visualization.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#top-level-specifications') padding
          td.table__td Number || Object
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | The default visualization padding, in pixels
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/config.html') config
          td.table__td Object
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | Vega-Lite configuration object.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#single') width
          td.table__td Number
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | The width of a visualization.
        tr.table__tr
          td.table__td: strong
            a(href='https://vega.github.io/vega-lite/docs/spec.html#single') height
          td.table__td Number
          td.table__td
          td.table__td
            | The height of a visualization.

